---
title: Caribbean-Spiced Beef Chilli with Coconut Rice & Charred Corn Salad
description: We’ve packed the signature flavours of the Caribbean into this mouth-watering beef chilli, served with fluffy coconut rice and a
crunchy charred corn salad.

